author: COMSOL
description: The Biot Poroelasticity example uses the Poroelasticity interface available in the Subsurface Flow Module to assess deformation of porous media that results from fluid withdrawal. The model builds on top of the Terzaghi compaction example and compares the results of the Terzaghi compaction and Biot poroelasticity analyses.
